x=i
(1+x)^n= p_0 + p_1 x + p_2 x^2+\cdots
p_0=1,\quad p_1=\dfrac{n}{1},\quad p_2=\dfrac{n(n-1)}{2!},\ldots
p_{0}-p_{2}+p_{4}-\dots=2^{n/2}\cos{\dfrac{n\pi}{4}}
p_{1}-p_{3}+p_{5}-\dots=2^{n/2}\sin{\dfrac{n\pi}{4}}
(1+i)^n
2^{n/2}*cos(\frac{n\pi}{4})
2^{n/2}*sin(\frac{n\pi}{4})
(1+i)^n
1+i=2^{1/2}(\cos(\frac{\pi}{4})+i\sin(\frac{\pi}{4}))
